# Integer Data type.
Integer is just another way of saying number.  

# we dont need to wrap numbers up in quote.
# we can just write them normally. 
12
123
3488
0
# when we have a number wuth a decimal it is considerd a float data type. 
12.03
23.56

4+4 
3/1

# Boolean Data type
# A data representation of true and false. 





0 # represents false

1 # represents true
